endpoint.response:
{ success, message, data: { widgets: Array<
  { type:'stat', key, label, value:number, format, subtitle?, icon? }
  | { type:'distribution', key, label, items:Array<{label,value}> }
  | { type:'trend', key, label, points:Array<{label,value}> }
> } }
Widget attesi: stat total/completed/failed/rows_imported/rows_modified/
rows_skipped; distribution by_status; trend mensile. Aggregati SOLO sui run
propri (user_id=actor) del dominio leads (resource='leads').

{ success, message, data: {
  resource: Record<string,bool>,            
  fields: Record<string,{ visible, editable, readonly, hidden, disabled, required }>,
  actions: Record<string,bool>              
} }
Tutti i campi sono visible+readonly (run non editabile a mano).
